    "Name": "Hammerhands HMH-RR",
    "Details": "The HMH-RR is a one-of-a-kind personal upgrade built by Riley Centrella of Riley's Rangers, a Magistracy-affiliated mercenary outfit, for her own exclusive use. Twin Ultra AC/10s replace the original Class-10s for doubled fire rate, backed by a Streak SRM 6 and twin ER Medium Lasers. Three jump jets give the 75-ton frame surprising repositioning ability. Every weapon system on the original frame was replaced with a more capable version.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Barrel Fist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
